      section#management
        h2 Management
        p I believe in working for, and in hiring, people that I can learn from.
        p.
          I believe that the jobs of management include making the organization comprehensible to individuals
          (by making it simpler where possible, and by simplifying its presentation where not);
          and making individuals comprehensible to the organization (by promoting their efforts and insuring that they
          stay connected and strategic).
        p.
          I believe in creating and maintaining alignment, where possible, between those activities that are fun,
          those that are fulfilling, and those that create value.
        //- Drudgery, like entropy, can’t be eliminated, but can be held at bay.
